-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Areas\">Grid Area</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Gutters\">Gutters</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Axis\">Grid Axis</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Rows\">Grid row</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Grid_Column\">Grid column</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"anleitungen","title":"Anleitungen","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"index\" id=\"sect6\">\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of Grid Layout</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Relationship_of_Grid_Layout\">Relationship of Grid Layout to other layout methods</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Line-based_Placement_with_CSS_Grid\">Layout using line-based placement</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Grid_Template_Areas\">Grid template areas</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Layout_using_Named_Grid_Lines\">Layout using named grid lines</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Auto-placement_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Auto-placement in CSS Grid Layout</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Box_Alignment_in_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Box alignment in CSS Grid Layout</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Logical_Values_and_Writing_Modes\">CSS Grid, Logical Values and Writing Modes</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_Layout_and_Accessibility\">CSS Grid Layout and accessibility</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/CSS_Grid_and_Progressive_Enhancement\">CSS Grid and progressive enhancement</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Realizing_common_layouts_using_CSS_Grid_Layout\">Realising common layouts using CSS Grid</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"externe_quellen","title":"Externe Quellen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://labs.jensimmons.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Beispiele von Jen Simmons</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://gridbyexample.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Grid by Example - eine Sammlung von Anwendungsbeispielen und Video-Tutorials</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://tympanus.net/codrops/css_reference/grid/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Codrops Grid Referenz</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Tools/Page_Inspector/How_to/Examine_grid_layouts\">Firefox DevTools CSS Grid Inspector</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://mozilladevelopers.github.io/playground/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Grid Playground</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Bemerkung</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-grid/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'CSS Grid Layout' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Grid Layout</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">Anwärter Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Einfaches Beispiel","id":"basic_example"},{"text":"Referenz","id":"referenz"},{"text":"Anleitungen","id":"anleitungen"},{"text":"Externe Quellen","id":"externe_quellen"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"}],"summary":"CSS Grid Layout zeichnet sich dadurch aus, dass eine Seite in Hauptbereiche unterteilt wird oder die Beziehung zwischen Teilen eines Steuerelements, das aus HTML-Grundelementen besteht, in Bezug auf Größe, Position und Layer definiert wird.","popularity":0.0015,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS Grid Layout","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"C